author: Chris Stuckmann
description:
From Osgood Perkins, the director of Longlegs & The Monkey, comes a new breed of nightmare. Don't miss the horror event of the season. KEEPER opens in theaters nationwide November 14th.

Chris Stuckmann reviews Bugonia, starring Emma Stone, Jesse Plemons, Aidan Delbis, Alicia Silverstone. Directed by Yorgos Lanthimos.
title: Bugonia - Movie Review
